2023 Comprehensive Guide to Buying a Dryer!
It lists several popular models from well-known domestic and international brands, and also provides a comparison of the functions of each model for reference, helping everyone to choose based on functional needs.
Here are a few function descriptions:
âœ…Appearance Color: Choose based on home style, generally available in white, silver, black, among which Miele's enamel body has the best texture and is not easily scratched;
âœ…Motor: Preferably inverter, more energy-saving;
âœ…Compressor: Preferably dual-rotor inverter, better drying effect;
âœ…Noise: Those concerned about noise can pay attention, among which Panasonic dryers have the least noise;
âœ…Capacity: Choose based on family size, generally 9KG is sufficient for most families, domestic models are usually 10KG;
âœ…Forward and Reverse Rotation: Prevents clothes from tangling and wrinkling;
âœ…Door Open Power Off: Higher safety;
âœ…Lint Collector: Deeply cleans clothes, generally available in heat pump dryers;
âœ…Leather and Fur Care: A function available in some high-end models, choose if you have more of such clothing;
âœ…Steam Wrinkle Removal: Some models come with steam ironing function, beneficial for shirts and similar garments;
âœ…Condenser Self-Cleaning: Reduces cleaning time, eliminates secondary pollution;
âœ…Quick Drying: Generally ranges from 20 minutes to 40 minutes, a bonus feature;
âœ…Stop When Dry: A function available in some brands, more intelligent, avoids under-drying or over-drying
